org.chirpradio.mobile
Class Track

java.lang.Object
  org.chirpradio.mobile.Track

public class Track
extends java.lang.Object

Encapsulates a track (song). Includes constructors to create an object including from a JSONObject. Keeps a static variable with the current track being played and a method to fetch it.

Author:
Chirag Patel

getCurrentTrack

public static Track getCurrentTrack()
Method to return the current playing track and store it in static member. Will attempt to fetch the track first, if it hasn't changed from the previous fetch (compares unique ID)

Returns:
the current track. Returns null if it hasn't changed
